'''中国图书'''（{{lang-en|Beijing Book Co., Inc.}}<ref name="ZarfesBloom2014">{{cite book|author1=David Zarfes|author2=Michael L. Bloom|title=Contracts and Commercial Transactions|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=46LfDgAAQBAJ&pg=PT399|date=30 October 2014|publisher=Wolters Kluwer|isbn=978-1-4548-2406-0|pages=399–|access-date=2020-07-11|archive-date=2020-07-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200718214835/https://books.google.com/books?id=46LfDgAAQBAJ&pg=PT399|dead-url=no}}</ref>），英文也译作'''北京图书公司'''<ref>{{cite book|title=中国出版年鉴|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=CXtGAAAAMAAJ|year=1995|publisher=商务印书馆|pages=190–|access-date=2020-07-20|archive-date=2020-08-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200811220429/https://books.google.com/books?id=CXtGAAAAMAAJ|dead-url=no}}</ref>，中文全称'''中国图书（美国）有限公司'''<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.cnpubg.com/overview/member/2012/1023/5307.shtml|title=中国图书（美国）有限公司|website=[[中国出版集团公司|中国出版集团公司]]|access-date=2020-07-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200605023934/http://www.cnpubg.com/overview/member/2012/1023/5307.shtml|archive-date=2020-06-05|dead-url=no}}</ref>，英文全称{{lang|en|China National Publications Beijing Book Co., Inc.}}，简作'''CNPBBCI'''或'''BBCI'''<ref>{{cite news|url=https://law.justia.com/cases/new-jersey/appellate-division-unpublished/2006/a1788-05-opn.html|title=Youngtech, Inc. v. Beijing Book Co., Inc.|date=2006-12-29|website=[[Justia|Justia]]|author=|access-date=2020-07-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200711224548/https://law.justia.com/cases/new-jersey/appellate-division-unpublished/2006/a1788-05-opn.html|archive-date=2020-07-11|dead-url=no}}</ref>，是一家位于[[美国|美国]][[新泽西州|新泽西州]]{{tsl|en|Linden, New Jersey|林登市}}的图书进出口公司<ref>{{cite book|title=Doing Business with China|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=_rQls9y7jk4C&pg=PA36|year=1989|publisher=U.S. Department of Commerce, International Trade Administration|pages=36–|access-date=2020-07-09|archive-date=2020-07-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200720061621/https://books.google.com/books?id=_rQls9y7jk4C&pg=PA36|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

该出版商成立于1981年<ref name="IncIncorporated2004">{{cite book|author1=Information Today Inc|author2=Information Today, Incorporated|title=Lmp 2005: The Directory of the American Book Publishing Industry With Industry Yellow Pages|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=K6DDUJkvu6IC|date=2004-01-01|publisher=Information Today, Incorporated|isbn=978-1-57387-203-4|pages=1622|access-date=2020-07-09|archive-date=2020-07-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200717211850/https://books.google.com/books?id=K6DDUJkvu6IC|dead-url=no}}</ref>，原为[[中国图书进出口总公司驻美国代表处|中国图书进出口总公司驻美国代表处]]<ref name="中国对外文化交流概览">{{cite book|title=中国对外文化交流概览, 1949-1991|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=tdaFAAAAIAAJ|year=1993|publisher=光明日报出版社|pages=539–|access-date=2020-07-20|archive-date=2020-08-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200811222843/https://books.google.com/books?id=tdaFAAAAIAAJ|dead-url=no}}</ref>，是一家[[中国人|中国人]]在美国创办的企业<ref>{{cite book|title=世界图书|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=q_UwAQAAIAAJ|year=1984|publisher=中国图书进口公司、世界图书编辑部|pages=10–|access-date=2020-07-20|archive-date=2020-08-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200811220313/https://books.google.com/books?id=q_UwAQAAIAAJ|dead-url=no}}</ref>，主要从事美国[[书刊|书刊]][[文献|文献]][[进口|进口]]业务<ref>{{cite book|title=世界图书|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=8XgWAAAAMAAJ|year=1984|pages=9–|access-date=2020-07-20|archive-date=2020-09-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200930154208/https://books.google.com/books?id=8XgWAAAAMAAJ|dead-url=no}}</ref>，包括向中国[[图书馆|图书馆]]进口美国出版物（[[书籍|书籍]]、[[期刊|期刊]]、其它系列和政府出版物），采购[[报纸|报纸]]、音乐产品、微型产品以及[[CD-ROM|CD-ROM]]等<ref name="Inc.2009">{{cite book|author=IBP, Inc.|title=US Book Distributors Directory Volume 2 Wholesalers|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=hPOxDwAAQBAJ&pg=PA33|date=2009-03-30|publisher=Lulu.com|isbn=978-1-4387-5364-5|pages=33–|access-date=2020-07-09|archive-date=2020-08-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200805011104/https://books.google.com/books?id=hPOxDwAAQBAJ&pg=PA33|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

中国图书隶属于[[中国图书进出口（集团）总公司|中国图书进出口（集团）总公司]]，是[[中国大陆|中国大陆]][[出版界|出版界]]第一家[[全资|全资]][[海外|海外]][[子公司|子公司]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://book.sina.com.cn/news/whxw/2019-12-26/doc-iihnzahi9939848.shtml|title=中国图书进出口（集团）总公司成立70周年大会在京举行|website=新浪读书|date=2019年12月26日|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191228140924/http://book.sina.com.cn/news/whxw/2019-12-26/doc-iihnzahi9939848.shtml|archive-date=2019-12-28|dead-url=no|accessdate=2020-07-20}}</ref>。该机构官网[[域名|域名]]cnpbbci.com注册于2002年6月20日<ref>{{cite web| url=https://whois.domaintools.com/cnpbbci.com| title=Whois Record for Cnpbbci.com| work=[[WHOIS|WHOIS]]| accessdate=2020-07-09| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200712193855/https://whois.domaintools.com/cnpbbci.com| archive-date=2020-07-12| dead-url=no}}</ref>。

